channel.description: The latest CVEs for Unknown -- Contact Form Email

item.title: CVE-2023-5955|2024-08-02T08:14:25.148Z -- unknown -- contact%20form%20email
item.description: The Contact Form Email WordPress plugin before 1.3.44 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)

item.title: CVE-2023-2718|2024-08-02T06:33:05.488Z -- unknown -- contact%20form%20email
item.description: The Contact Form Email WordPress plugin before 1.3.38 does not escape submitted values before displaying them in the HTML, leading to a Stored XSS vulnerability.
